\begin_layout Standard
Expression for conformation free energy 
\begin_inset Formula $A(X)$
\end_inset

 via the logarithm of the partition function, Eq.
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:conformation-free-energy"

\end_inset

