 In such a process the free energy derivative is an average of the potential
 derivative over constrained ensemble 
\begin_inset Formula $X=\text{const}$
\end_inset

.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "book:hansen76"

\end_inset

