 type 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\rho_{\alpha}(\vec{r})=\sum_{i\in\alpha}\delta(\vec{r}-\vec{r}_{i}),
\end{equation}

\end_inset

or, in the mean field approach, the site distribution functions 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho_{\alpha}$
\end_inset

